    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>HuleEdu</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Welcome to HuleEdu!</h2>
            <p>Hello {{ first_name|default(user_name)|default('there') }},</p>
            <p>Welcome to HuleEdu! We're excited to have you join our educational community.</p>
            <p>With HuleEdu, you can:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Submit and manage your academic work</li>
                <li>Receive detailed feedback on your submissions</li>
                <li>Track your progress and improvement</li>
                <li>Collaborate with peers and instructors</li>
            </ul>
            <p>To get started, click the button below to explore your dashboard:</p>
            <p style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="{{ dashboard_link|default('https://app.huleedu.com/dashboard') }}" class="button">Go to Dashboard</a>
            </p>
            <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>
            <p>Thank you for choosing HuleEdu!</p>
        </div>
